ActFirst Nations Fiscal Management Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the First Nations Fiscal Management Act
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE FIRST NATIONS FISCAL MANAGEMENT ACT in order to add the following nine First Nations: Ebb and Flow (MB), Fisher River (MB), Heiltsuk (BC), Mistawasis (SK), Norway House Cree Nation (MB), Peguis (MB), Penticton Indian Band (BC), St. Theresa Point (MB) and Wet'suwet'en First Nation (BC).
